About This Music Sheet

Lightning’s Theme (Final Fantasy) is a song by Masashi Hamauzu. Use your computer keyboard to play Lightning’s Theme (Final Fantasy) music sheet on Virtual Piano. This is an Intermediate song and requires a lot of practice to play well. The song Lightning’s Theme (Final Fantasy) is classified in the genres: Songs From Games, Final Fantasy on Virtual Piano. You can also find other similar songs using Animation, Fantasy.
